oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Campground School and Church
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Campground School and Church, Burrows Cove. A large group of children and adults stand outside the building.
Named this because it used to be a Native American campground and soldiers later used this area for maneuvers.
